Sebastian Arcelus https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sebastian_Arcelus 0 Sebastian Carlos Arcelus (born November 5, 1976) is an American actor, best known for his roles as Lucas Goodwin in the Netflix TV series House of Cards from 2013 to 2016 and Jay Whitman in the CBS TV series Madam Secretary.
